FedComment is a research and educational tool for analysing public comments
submitted on US federal regulations. It is not affiliated with, endorsed by,
or sponsored by any US government agency. Data is sourced from public US
federal APIs (Federal Register, Regulations.gov) and bears the attribution
and licensing of those sources.
